er-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:11.0pt;">: </span><span style="font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-size:11.0pt;">성범죄</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:11.0pt;">, </span><span style="font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-size:11.0pt;">아동학대</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:11.0pt;">, </span><span style="font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-size:11.0pt;">노인학대 범죄전력자 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:11.0pt;">(</span><span style="font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-size:11.0pt;">채용시 관련서류 확인함</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:11.0pt;">)</span></p><p class="0"><span style="font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;mso-hansi-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-weight:bold;font-size:11.0pt;">□ </span><span style="font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-weight:bold;font-size:11.0pt;">근무시간</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-size:11.0pt;"> </span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:11.0pt;">: </span><span style="font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-size:11.0pt;">평일 오전 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:11.0pt;">9</span><span style="font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font